Package: oncoAgent
Title: Agentic AI-Driven Oncology Target Discovery from Multi-Omics Data
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Dany", "Mukesha", , "danymukesha@gmail.com", 
            role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-9514-751X"))
Description: A semi-autonomous research system that integrates multi-omics
    data (genomics, transcriptomics, CRISPR screens, drug sensitivity) with
    literature mining and clinical outcomes to identify and prioritize
    oncology drug targets. Features adaptive agentic workflows with gap
    detection, hypothesis generation, and benchmarking against known cancer
    gene sets (COSMIC, Open Targets). Designed for industry-grade target
    discovery pipelines at pharma scale.
